How to use Hugo:

1. Update posts under Blog -> content folder
2. Check it with 'hugo serve' command
3. Generate static pages with 'hugo -D'
4. Push the generated files to master branch.
5. Note: the directories 'theme' , 'content' are part of git ignore. [May need backing up]


